ible and computationally tractable way to include enzyme\nkinetics into constraint-based metabolic models, where kinetics have usually\nbeen ignored or oversimplified.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 1 Apr 2016 08:48:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-08"}
